metadata.description: By popular demand, it's the triumphant return of Gold Digger's own Odd Couple: seven-year-old genius Tifanny 'Gia -- half were-cheetah and half alien Kryn -- and her bestest buddy, Charlotte Pincer -- full-grown, genetically designed harpy with the mind of young teen. They're back in class at A.P.S.-001, the school for super-beings and super-brains, where more super-weirdness and super-fun are filling the curriculum!
metadata.name: Gold Digger: Tifanny & Charlotte Second Semester, Vol. 2
